.SH Name
.SP 5 5
event_combat -  This event is generated when a combat message occurs.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void event_combat(object thing,
string message,
object * exclude,
int verbose)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^thing%^RESET%^ - the thing generateing the event.
%^BOLD%^message%^RESET%^ - the message to be displayed.
%^BOLD%^exclude%^RESET%^ - objects not to show this message to.
%^BOLD%^verbose%^RESET%^ - is the message considered verbose?

.EI

